pair_coeff * * oxrna2/stk     seqdep 300.0 oxrna2_real.cgdna
Reading oxdna potential (stk) file oxrna2_real.cgdna with DATE: 2024-03-04
pair_coeff * * oxrna2/hbond   seqdep oxrna2_real.cgdna
