pair_coeff 2 3 oxrna2/hbond   seqdep oxrna2_real.cgdna
Reading oxdna potential (hbond) file oxrna2_real.cgdna with DATE: 2024-03-04
pair_coeff 3 4 oxrna2/hbond   seqdep oxrna2_real.cgdna
